            <div type="edition" xml:space="preserve"><head>Text</head><ab><lb n="1"/>
                <expan><abbr>L</abbr><ex>ucius</ex></expan> Plotidius <expan><abbr>L</abbr><ex>uci</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>f</abbr><ex>ilius</ex></expan> <lb n="2"/>Lemonia Vitalis do<lb break="no" n="3"/>mo Bononia <lb n="4"/>miles <expan><abbr>leg</abbr><ex>ionis</ex></expan> XV <expan><abbr>Apoll</abbr><ex>inaris</ex></expan> <lb n="5"/><expan><abbr>n<am>n</am></abbr><ex>orum</ex></expan> L <expan><abbr>stip</abbr><ex>endiorum</ex></expan> XXIII <expan><abbr>h</abbr><ex>ic</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>s</abbr><ex>itus</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>e</abbr><ex>st</ex></expan> <lb n="6"/>Annia Maxima <lb n="7"/>viro suo cariss<lb break="no" n="8"/>imo posuit structo<lb break="no" n="9"/>ria asciam norma<lb break="no" n="10"/>m
            </ab></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Z. 2: kleines O zwischen M und N, kleines A zwischen I und V. M außer Z. 2 nach links geneigt. Im Giebelfeld von Schlangen gerahmtes Gorgoneion, darunter Brustbild in Reliefnische. Soldat in tunica und paenula, bartlos, mit gladius. Im Inschriftfeld ascia, regula, scalprum, norma, circinus. (B): Ubl: Z. 2/3: &amp;apos;Lemonia (tribu) do/mo&amp;apos;.</p>
            </div>
